
  EPA STORM WATER MANAGEMENT MODEL - VERSION 5.2 (Build 5.2.4)
  ------------------------------------------------------------

  Demonstrates the fix for a v5.1.013 bug that skipped the first rain gage when checking if two gages have 
  the same station ID but use different data files. Running this file now correctly produces "Error 156: 
  ambiguous station ID for Rain Gage 2" since Gage 2 has the same station ID as Gage 1 but a different rainfall file. 
  
